body_html: This is unlikely to be a bug in TensorFlow. I would suggest printing out session.graph. Presumably it will be different from out.graph. This is probably fixable by passing graph=something when making the session, but further details should be asked about on StackOverflow, not here.

body: This is unlikely to be a bug in TensorFlow.  I would suggest printing out `session.graph`.  Presumably it will be different from `out.graph`.  This is probably fixable by passing `graph=something` when making the session, but further details should be asked about on StackOverflow, not here.
